
RHid  -- Ruby USB HID class access library

NISHI Takao <zophos@koka-in.org>

= What's RHid

RHid is Ruby USB HID class access library.

= Requirements

* Windows XP/vista/2003
* Ruby 1.8 or higher (MSWIN/Cygwin)

